as they are holy rauisshed aud geuin to the contemplacion
of inuisible thyngꝭ. For as worldlyngꝭ haue richesse
in best reputacion, next therto estemyng the weale
of theyr bodies, and lest regardyng the profite of theyr
soules, in case thei regarde it at all, for some of them beleue
